{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"4e828d2d-7408-5169-8935-a661dd24645b","excerpt":"What's new?I have been spending a lot of time doing research, working on drawings & artwork, and writing pages for the next book in the…","frontmatter":{"title":"Updates and New Drawings for Genesis Book Series","date":"26 May 2019","path":"/updates-new-drawings","author":"Jered Higgins","excerpt":"I have been spending a lot of time doing research, working on drawings & artwork, and writing pages for the next book in the Genesis series. I put together 50 pages of notes I had, completed the first two chapters of the book, and updated several drawings. All the previous artwork was done on paper using mixed media, but since the new book will also be available in digital format I decided to recreate all of my drawings from scratch. ","tags":["blog","genesis","drawings"],"coverImage":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.34154090548054,"src":"/static/55586b999c95c4a2589192090913076a/bc3a8/new-drawings-preview.jpg","srcSet":"/static/55586b999c95c4a2589192090913076a/d278e/new-drawings-preview.jpg 200w,\n/static/55586b999c95c4a2589192090913076a/8539d/new-drawings-preview.jpg 400w,\n/static/55586b999c95c4a2589192090913076a/bc3a8/new-drawings-preview.jpg 800w,\n/static/55586b999c95c4a2589192090913076a/81ef8/new-drawings-preview.jpg 1200w,\n/static/55586b999c95c4a2589192090913076a/989b1/new-drawings-preview.jpg 1600w,\n/static/55586b999c95c4a2589192090913076a/7de88/new-drawings-preview.jpg 1689w","sizes":"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"}}}}}}]}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"tag":"drawings","pageNumber":0,"humanPageNumber":1,"skip":0,"limit":5,"numberOfPages":1,"previousPagePath":"","nextPagePath":""}}